parameter 1: The original premiere on MTV was followed by a truncated version of 'Behind the Scenes at Daria' to fill up the time slot.

parameter 9: When shown on the cable channel Noggin in July 2002, 'Is It Fall Yet?' was significantly re-edited to fit the demographic of the channel. With so much taken out, most of the extra footage seen only in the premiere and on the VHS/DVD release was spliced back in to fill up the time.
